# Strategy-based Investment Simulation System — 아키텍처 및 Java 개념 분석

## 1. 시스템 전체 구조

프로젝트는 **6개의 도메인 패키지**로 구성된 멀티 모듈 투자 시뮬레이션 시스템입니다.

```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph engine["🏗️ engine 패키지"]
        DS[DailySimulation]
        EN[Engine]
        AS[AllocationService]
    end

    subgraph strategy["📊 strategy 패키지"]
        ST["«interface» Startegy"]
        SMS[SimpleMomentumStrategy]
        PD[PortfolioDecision]
        SIG["«enum» Signal"]
    end

    subgraph risk["🛡️ risk 패키지"]
        RP["«interface» RiskPolicy"]
        BRP[BasicRiskPolicy]
        RS[RiskScore]
    end

    subgraph market["📈 market 패키지"]
        MDP["«interface» MarketDataProvider"]
        MSS[MarketSnapshot]
    end

    subgraph order["📝 order 패키지"]
        OF[OrderFactory]
        ORD[Order]
        OT["«enum» OrderType"]
    end

    subgraph portfolio["💰 portfolio 패키지"]
        PF[Portfolio]
        POS[Position]
    end

    DS -->|"위임"| EN
    EN -->|"의사결정 요청"| ST
    SMS -.->|implements| ST
    EN -->|"리스크 평가"| RP
    BRP -.->|implements| RP
    EN -->|"비중 배분"| AS
    EN -->|"주문 생성"| OF
    EN -->|"주문 적용"| PF
    PF -->|"보유"| POS
    OF -->|"생성"| ORD
    ST -->|"반환"| PD
    RP -->|"반환"| RS
    PD -->|"포함"| SIG
    ORD -->|"포함"| OT
    EN -->|"시장 데이터 수신"| MSS
```

---

## 2. 시스템 작동 원리 (실행 흐름)

`DailySimulation.run()`이 시뮬레이션의 진입점이며, 날짜별 [MarketSnapshot](file:///c:/Users/alstj/OneDrive/%EB%B0%94%ED%83%95%20%ED%99%94%EB%A9%B4/%EB%AF%BC%EC%84%B1/Dev/Strategy-based%20Investment%20Simulation%20System/core/src/main/java/quantengine/domain/market/MarketSnapshot.java#6-35) 리스트를 순회하면서 `Engine.process()`에 위임합니다.

### Engine.process() 5단계 파이프라인

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant DS as DailySimulation
    participant EN as Engine
    participant ST as Strategy
    participant RP as RiskPolicy
    participant AS as AllocationService
    participant OF as OrderFactory
    participant PF as Portfolio

    DS->>EN: process(snapshot)

    Note over EN,ST: ① 의사결정
    EN->>ST: decide(current, previous)
    ST-->>EN: List<PortfolioDecision>

    Note over EN: ② BUY/SELL 분리 (HOLD 필터링)

    Note over EN,PF: ③ SELL 먼저 처리 (cash 확보)
    loop 각 SELL decision
        EN->>RP: evaluate(decision, snapshot)
        RP-->>EN: RiskScore
        EN->>OF: from(decision, amount, snapshot)
        OF-->>EN: Order
        EN->>PF: apply(sellOrder)
    end

    Note over EN,PF: ④ BUY 리스크 검증 + 비중 배분
    loop 각 BUY decision
        EN->>RP: evaluate(decision, snapshot)
    end
    EN->>AS: allocate(buyDecisions, riskScore, portfolio)
    AS-->>EN: Map<ticker, amount>

    Note over EN,PF: ⑤ BUY 주문 생성 및 적용
    loop 각 배분 결과
        EN->>OF: from(decision, allocatedAmount, snapshot)
        OF-->>EN: Order
        EN->>PF: apply(buyOrder)
    end

    EN->>EN: previousSnapshot = snapshot
```

| 단계 | 설명 | 관련 클래스 |
|------|------|------------|
| ① Strategy 의사결정 | 현재/이전 스냅샷을 비교하여 각 종목에 대해 BUY/SELL/HOLD 결정 | [Startegy](file:///c:/Users/alstj/OneDrive/%EB%B0%94%ED%83%95%20%ED%99%94%EB%A9%B4/%EB%AF%BC%EC%84%B1/Dev/Strategy-based%20Investment%20Simulation%20System/core/src/main/java/quantengine/domain/strategy/Startegy.java#7-18), [SimpleMomentumStrategy](file:///c:/Users/alstj/OneDrive/%EB%B0%94%ED%83%95%20%ED%99%94%EB%A9%B4/%EB%AF%BC%EC%84%B1/Dev/Strategy-based%20Investment%20Simulation%20System/core/src/main/java/quantengine/domain/strategy/SimpleMomentumStrategy.java#18-46) |
| ② HOLD 필터링 | Stream API로 HOLD를 제외하고 BUY/SELL로 분리 | [Engine](file:///c:/Users/alstj/OneDrive/%EB%B0%94%ED%83%95%20%ED%99%94%EB%A9%B4/%EB%AF%BC%EC%84%B1/Dev/Strategy-based%20Investment%20Simulation%20System/core/src/main/java/quantengine/domain/engine/Engine.java#28-110) |
| ③ SELL 처리 | SELL 주문을 먼저 실행하여 매도 대금으로 cash 확보 | [RiskPolicy](file:///c:/Users/alstj/OneDrive/%EB%B0%94%ED%83%95%20%ED%99%94%EB%A9%B4/%EB%AF%BC%EC%84%B1/Dev/Strategy-based%20Investment%20Simulation%20System/core/src/main/java/quantengine/domain/risk/RiskPolicy.java#6-10), [OrderFactory](file:///c:/Users/alstj/OneDrive/%EB%B0%94%ED%83%95%20%ED%99%94%EB%A9%B4/%EB%AF%BC%EC%84%B1/Dev/Strategy-based%20Investment%20Simulation%20System/core/src/main/java/quantengine/domain/order/OrderFactory.java#7-30), [Portfolio](file:///c:/Users/alstj/OneDrive/%EB%B0%94%ED%83%95%20%ED%99%94%EB%A9%B4/%EB%AF%BC%EC%84%B1/Dev/Strategy-based%20Investment%20Simulation%20System/core/src/main/java/quantengine/domain/portfolio/Portfolio.java#9-68) |
| ④ BUY 비중 배분 | confidence 비율 기반으로 가용 cash를 종목별로 배분 | [AllocationService](file:///c:/Users/alstj/OneDrive/%EB%B0%94%ED%83%95%20%ED%99%94%EB%A9%B4/%EB%AF%BC%EC%84%B1/Dev/Strategy-based%20Investment%20Simulation%20System/core/src/main/java/quantengine/domain/engine/AllocationService.java#14-56), [RiskScore](file:///c:/Users/alstj/OneDrive/%EB%B0%94%ED%83%95%20%ED%99%94%EB%A9%B4/%EB%AF%BC%EC%84%B1/Dev/Strategy-based%20Investment%20Simulation%20System/core/src/main/java/quantengine/domain/risk/RiskScore.java#5-52) |
| ⑤ BUY 주문 실행 | 배분된 금액으로 Order를 생성하고 Portfolio에 적용 | [OrderFactory](file:///c:/Users/alstj/OneDrive/%EB%B0%94%ED%83%95%20%ED%99%94%EB%A9%B4/%EB%AF%BC%EC%84%B1/Dev/Strategy-based%20Investment%20Simulation%20System/core/src/main/java/quantengine/domain/order/OrderFactory.java#7-30), [Portfolio](file:///c:/Users/alstj/OneDrive/%EB%B0%94%ED%83%95%20%ED%99%94%EB%A9%B4/%EB%AF%BC%EC%84%B1/Dev/Strategy-based%20Investment%20Simulation%20System/core/src/main/java/quantengine/domain/portfolio/Portfolio.java#9-68) |

